name: Phi Traveler Set
short_description: Phi Travel Set is a unique travel essentials collection designed to help you present your values and express your style through our brand ideology, while on the go.
long_description: The set includes a passport case and a luggage tag in a special Phi gift box. This unique Phi style design features our logo print representing our brand philosophy , while an array of organized interior pockets ensures you always have your essential documents organized. The passport case has inserted pockets for card slots and travel documents and the luggage tag includes personal info card inserted, for your own piece of mind while traveling.Travel with Phi Style and leave footprints wherever you go.
